http://webcam-osx.sourceforge.net/ macam is a driver for USB webcams on Mac OS X.
It allows hundreds of USB webcams to be used by many Mac OS X video-aware applications.
The aim is to support as many webcams as possible.
here is the link to a list of web cams supported including many, many logitech cams http://webcam-osx.sourceforge.net/cameras/index.php
